        <abstract>
            <para>This presentation provides coverage of how to package a JPA persistence unit
                 within an EJB or WAR deployed to the server. It covers the resources involved
                 and how they can be injected into the beans of the data tier.
            </para>
        </abstract>
    </bookinfo>
